### Introduction

In this chapter you will learn how to create plots with the _ggplot2_ package (part of the tidyverse).

To meet this chapter's learning objectives, please complete the respective exercise sheet. The instructions below will guide you through the process of solving the exercise sheet.

### Step 1

Briefly check out the [exercise sheet](C4_exercise.html){target="blank"} for chapter 4 to get an impression of what you need to learn/know to solve it.

### Step 2

Solve Tasks 1-7 of the exercise sheet.

### Step 3

Watch the following YouTube Video: 
[An Introduction to Data Visualization](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HPJn1CMvtmI&list=PLtL57Fdbwb_C6RS0JtBojTNOMVlgpeJkS&index=1){target="blank"}

### Step 4

Do the “Exploratory Data Analysis” tutorial offered in the posit Cloud:
[Exploratory Data Analysis](https://posit.cloud/learn/primers/3.1){target="blank"}

### Step 5

Solve task 8 of the exercise sheet.

### Step 6

Do the “Bar Charts” tutorial offered in the posit Cloud:
[Bar Charts](https://posit.cloud/learn/primers/3.2){target="blank"}

**Comment:** It is sufficient if you focus on the subchapters “Bar Charts” and “Aesthetics”. 

### Step 7

Solve tasks 9-10 of the exercise sheet.

### Step 8

Do the “Histograms” tutorial offered in the RStudio Cloud: 
[Histograms](https://rstudio.cloud/learn/primers/3.3){target="blank"}

**Comment:** It is sufficient to focus on the subchapter “Histograms”.

### Step 9

Solve tasks 11-12 of the exercise sheet.

### Step 10

Watch the following Video: 
[Density Plots](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UGeJ73k6BGs){target="blank"}

### Step 11

Solve tasks 13-14.

### Step 12

Watch the following Video: 
[Boxplots](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EZjkg_hsh-w&list=PLkrJrLs7xfbVbI1WHs8FfkOoFvtiI6EXd&index=8){target="blank"}

### Step 13

Solve task 15.

### Step 14

Watch the following Video: 
[Scatter Plots](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DjORoUDMLD4&list=PLkrJrLs7xfbVbI1WHs8FfkOoFvtiI6EXd&index=10){target="blank"}

### Step 15

Solve task 16.

### Step 16

Watch the following Video:
[Smoother](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P2_qYBV1Byc&list=PLkrJrLs7xfbVbI1WHs8FfkOoFvtiI6EXd&index=11){target="blank"}

### Step 17

Solve task 17.

### Step 18

Watch the following Video:
[Draw Lines](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dD51z8MN1GI){target="blank"}

### Step 19

Solve Task 18

### Step 20

Compare your solutions to the [sample solution](C4_solution.html){target="blank"} for exercise sheet 4.

